summary: A simple tattoo retex for the female body. I believe it\'s CBBE
descriptionHtml:
~~Description
After years of being a member of the nexus I decided to do at least something.
So here\'s a female body texture with transmutation circles, a Templar cross, and the humunculus sign in the chest like Lust used to have in Fullmetal Alchemist.

If anyone want\'s me to do something else, please PM me or leave a comment.

~~Copyright~~
I made each design from scratch in photoshop except the whole body. With all permission I ask would like to ask Caliente for his approval. I take no ownership of the body except the designs in it.

~~INSTALLATION~~
*!Make sure to make a backup!
Place in C:/Program files/Steam/Steamapps/Common/Skyrim/Data/Textures/Actors/(and depending on which body of a race you want to change you place it there.
author: Dante
